erties, which has implications for the subsequent evolution of the\nsatellites systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2009 20:11:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2009 06:18:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
