ibute to alleviate the well\nknown problem of the large zero point energy due to quantum matter fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2009 11:36:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Aug 2009 13:15:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-08-26"}
