 found, consisting of 28 faint RR\nLyraes centered on Galactic coordinates (80 deg, -55 deg) and with distances of\n~ 80 kpc. The total stellar mass in the Pisces Overdensity is ~10000 solar\nmasses and its metallicity is [Fe/H] ~ -1.5.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jun 2009 15:54:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-12-08"}
